text:
There are 2 national security problems with China’s control of TikTok, Hayman Capital’s Kyle Bass says:
-The Chinese government has “aggressive data collection” policies
-TikTok’s algorithm can “influence the thinking and the minds of U.S. youth” https://t.co/sgWqyIvsfR https://t.co/BmYxZdanfE
